#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:262
msgid "BuddyPress Member Reviews"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:264
msgid ""
"This plugin allows only site members to add reviews to the buddypress "
"members on the site and even rate the member’s profile out of 5 points with "
"multiple review criteria."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:270
msgid "BuddyPress Group Reviews"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:272
msgid ""
"This plugin allows the BuddyPress Members to give reviews to the BuddyPress "
"groups on the site. The review form allows the users to give text review, "
"even rate the group on the basis of multiple criterias."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:278
msgid "BuddyPress Favorite Notification"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:280
msgid ""
"BuddyPress Favorite Notification adds a notification for BuddyPress "
"activity."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:286
msgid "Custom Email Options"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:288
msgid "Override default email options of Worpdress."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:294
msgid "BuddyPress Checkins"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:296
msgid ""
"This plugin allows BuddyPress members to share their location when they are "
"posting activities, you can add places where you visited, nearby locations "
"based on google places."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:302
msgid "BuddyPress Job Manager"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:304
msgid ""
"Incorporates BuddyPress with the WP Job Manager plugin by creating specific "
"tabs in employer’s and candidate’s profiles."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:310
msgid "BuddyPress user ToDo List"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:312
msgid ""
"This plugin allows you to create your personal task list with timestamp. "
"You can mark them complete when you are done with them. It will also send "
"reminder when you have any overdue task."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:318
msgid "Shortcodes for BuddyPress"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:320
msgid ""
"This plugin will add an extended feature to the big name “BuddyPress” that "
"will generate Shortcode for Listing Activity Streams , Members and Groups "
"on any post/page in website."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:326
msgid "Woo Open Graph"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:328
msgid ""
"This plugin will add an extended feature to the big name “WooCommerce” that "
"will adds well executed and accurate Open Graph Meta Tags to your site with "
"title,description and WooCommerce featured image."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:334
msgid "BuddyPress Lock"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:336
msgid ""
"This plugin allows the administrator to lock the certain parts of their "
"site. It help to create private BuddyPress community by locking certain "
"BuddyPress Components, WordPress Pages, Custom Post Types for public view "
"without using any membership plugin."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:342
msgid "Woo Audio Preview"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:344
msgid ""
"This plugin Allows playing the audio files in sample mode to prevent "
"unauthorized downloading of the audio files. It helps to display sample "
"files at single product page."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:350
msgid "WordPress System Log"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:352
msgid ""
"This plugin helps administrators of the site see their environment on which "
"the site is currently running that includes WordPress environment, tha "
"database it requires, Server Environment and the plugins installed and "
"activated on the site."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:358
msgid "BP Post From Anywhere"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:360
msgid ""
"This plugin will generate shortcode and widgets for post updates section "
"for activities so you can post update from anywhere, it might be sidebar, "
"some page or any template file."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:366
msgid "Woo Document Preview"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:368
msgid ""
"This will allow you to add document preview at single product page. Which "
"helps to offer more better idea when you are selling ebooks, pdf or some "
"documents."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:374
msgid "WordPress Media Category"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:376
#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:392
msgid ""
"This plugin helps administrators of the site categorize their wordpress "
"media."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:382
msgid "Woo Price Quotes"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:384
msgid ""
"This plugin helps in quoting the products that admin wishes to hide its "
"purchasing details."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:390
msgid "EDD Service Extended"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:398
msgid "WB Ads Rotator with Split Test"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:400
msgid ""
"This plugin is designed for the SPLIT TESTING, you can check performance of "
"your ads layout and on the basis of them you can select one of them for "
"your regular use."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:418
msgid "BuddyPress Moderation Pro"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:419
msgid ""
"BuddyPress Community Moderation offers a solution for site owners to keep "
"their communities straight. With community policing strategy, members of "
"the community have an option for moderation sitewide by attaching flags to "
"content created within the various components."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:424
msgid "BuddyPress Polls"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:425
msgid ""
"Use BuddyPress Polls plugin to create polls inside the activity, let your "
"user response to your polls. Members can create pools like activities, "
"easily votes on them."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:430
msgid "BuddyPress Resume Manager"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:431
msgid ""
"BuddyPress Resume Manager adds a separate BuddyPress Resume menu at a "
"user’s BuddyPress Profile Page to display individual member resume. We have "
"added predefined fields for the resumes and site admin and enable and "
"disable them."
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:436
msgid "BuddyPress Profanity"
msgstr ""

#: admin/wbcom/class-wbcom-admin-settings.php:437
msgid ""
